des: Tim Tawa doubles (1) on a ground ball to left fielder Isiah Gilliam.   Jose Fernandez scores.    Kevin Graham scores.    Tim Tawa to 3rd.  Tim Tawa advances to 3rd, on a throwing error by left fielder Isiah Gilliam.
David Martin singles on a ground ball to center fielder Jonatan Clase.   Kevin Sim scores.    Jose Fernandez to 3rd.
Manuel Pena lines out to left fielder Isiah Gilliam.
Jose Fernandez reaches on a fielding error by shortstop Ryan Bliss.   Kevin Sim to 2nd.
